title: 852. Favorite Week 1 Revenge Storylines + Most Intriguing Divisions
itunes:title: 852. Favorite Week 1 Revenge Storylines + Most Intriguing Divisions
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys each give their most intriguing division ahead of the regular season. Next, the pair break down their favorite Week 1 revenge storylines. To wrap up the show, the duo discuss Geno Smith being named the Seahawks starting quarterback.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
